  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Reclaim your games from the evil Pickle-Arms Johnson!</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/09ab639372222bd9b2981f71c7ebcb8e.poster.avif?t=1506898818\" width=614 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/09ab639372222bd9b2981f71c7ebcb8e.webm?t=1506898818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/09ab639372222bd9b2981f71c7ebcb8e.mp4?t=1506898818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Jumpfist is a fast paced platformer that will test even the most seasoned of gamers! </strong><br><br><strong>Jump, punch, slide & elbow-drop your way through mayhem and reclaim your stolen games!<br><br>You like fast paced platformers do you? <br><br>You want a challenge you say?<br><br>JumpFist is designed to test you, challenge you and yes....break you (legit i threw my controller down a few times beta testing)<br><br>Jump, slide, punch and elbow drop your way through 40 levels!<br><br>Too hard? Jump with a friend, local co-op available.<br><br>Beat the developer times and become the fastest!<br><br>Hilarious death commentary!</strong><br><br><strong><u>JumpFist is here! Get that parkour today!</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/6e5e88a59a191bc44a2955fecaf235ba.poster.avif?t=1506898818\" width=614 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/6e5e88a59a191bc44a2955fecaf235ba.webm?t=1506898818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/707470/extras/6e5e88a59a191bc44a2955fecaf235ba.mp4?t=1506898818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
